Project Journey Details Step By Step :-

1. Water Level Indicator System :-
- This is an Acadmic Project but it is also Done in Group of 2 Me and one is Raj Patel. 
- Connections :-
| Item                              | Pin / Probe | Connect To                     |
| --------------------------------- | ----------- | ------------------------------ |
| **Common Probe (Bottom of Tank)** | GND Wire    | Battery –                      |
| **Low Level Probe**               | Signal      | 10kΩ → Base of Q1              |
| **Middle Level Probe**            | Signal      | 10kΩ → Base of Q2              |
| **High Level Probe**              | Signal      | 10kΩ → Base of Q3              |
| **Q1 (BC547 – Low Level)**        | Collector   | Green LED +                    |
|                                   | Emitter     | GND                            |
| **Q2 (BC547 – Mid Level)**        | Collector   | Yellow LED +                   |
|                                   | Emitter     | GND                            |
| **Q3 (BC547 – High Level)**       | Collector   | Red LED + + Buzzer +           |
|                                   | Emitter     | GND                            |
| **Green LED –**                   | –           | GND via 220Ω                   |
| **Yellow LED –**                  | –           | GND via 220Ω                   |
| **Red LED –**                     | –           | GND via 220Ω                   |
| **Buzzer –**                      | –           | GND                            |
| **Battery +**                     | +V          | All LED + (through collectors) |
| **Battery –**                     | GND         | Common probe + all emitters    |


For Making this Simple Projet i use  a first Making this like a Board but than facing it's all parts like Soldering and all things i use than the Breadboard.


