-Connections :-
| Module                 | Pin         | Connects To                                      |
| ---------------------- | ----------- | ------------------------------------------------ |
| **HC-SR04 Ultrasonic** | VCC         | Arduino 5V                                       |
|                        | GND         | Arduino GND                                      |
|                        | TRIG        | Arduino D9                                       |
|                        | ECHO        | Arduino D10                                      |
| **HC-05 Bluetooth**    | VCC         | Arduino 5V                                       |
|                        | GND         | Arduino GND                                      |
|                        | TXD         | Arduino D2                                       |
|                        | RXD         | Arduino D3                                       |
| **L298N Motor Driver** | ENA         | Arduino D5 (PWM)                                 |
|                        | IN1         | Arduino D6                                       |
|                        | IN2         | Arduino D7                                       |
|                        | IN3         | Arduino D8                                       |
|                        | IN4         | Arduino D11                                      |
|                        | ENB         | Arduino D4 (PWM)                                 |
|                        | +12V        | Battery +                                        |
|                        | GND         | Battery – (also Arduino GND – **common ground**) |
| **Motors**             | OUT1 & OUT2 | Left Motor                                       |
|                        | OUT3 & OUT4 | Right Motor                                      |


